---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ServiceExplore from '../../components/ServiceExplore.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Crowns & Bridges — Oasis Dental Care, Huntington Beach"
  description="Custom dental crowns and bridges in Huntington Beach. Same-day crowns available. Restore your smile with Dr. Jason Fu at Oasis Dental Care. Call (714) 893-2106."
  page="services"
>

<section class="phero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumbs"><a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/services">Services</a><span class="sep">/</span><span style="color:#cfe6e2">Crowns &amp; Bridges</span></div>
    <span class="tag">Restorative dentistry</span>
    <h1>Crowns &amp; Bridges</h1>
    <p>Restore strength, function, and a natural appearance.</p>
    <div class="acts">
      <a class="btn" href="/contact">Book a consultation <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:7148932106">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pad">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="split">
      <div>

        <div class="img-ph reveal">
          <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
          <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
          <span class="img-ph-desc">Close-up of natural-looking crown or restored smile</span>
        </div>

        <div class="prose reveal">
          <span class="tag">Overview</span>
          <h2>Custom-made to match your natural smile.</h2>
          <p>Crowns protect and rebuild damaged teeth. Bridges fill the gap left by missing teeth. Both are custom-made to match your natural smile and restore full function.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose reveal" style="margin-top:48px">
          <h3>Crowns</h3>
          <p>A crown is a custom cap placed over a damaged tooth to restore its shape, strength, and appearance. Common uses include cracked or worn teeth, teeth after root canal therapy, and teeth too damaged for a filling.</p>

          <div class="img-ph reveal">
            <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
            <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
            <span class="img-ph-desc">Diagram or photo of crown placement — clean and professional</span>
          </div>

          <h3>Bridges</h3>
          <p>A bridge fills the gap from one or more missing teeth, anchored to surrounding healthy teeth or implants. It restores bite function, prevents teeth from shifting, and maintains facial structure.</p>

          <div class="img-ph reveal">
            <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
            <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
            <span class="img-ph-desc">Bridge illustration or before/after photo</span>
          </div>

          <h3>What to Expect</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Consultation and digital imaging</li>
            <li>Tooth preparation and impression</li>
            <li>Temporary crown/bridge while permanent is made</li>
            <li>Final placement and bite adjustment</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Same-Day Crowns</h3>
          <p>We offer advanced CAD/CAM same-day crown technology—no second appointment, no temporary crown. Ask us if you qualify.</p>

          <div class="img-ph reveal">
            <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
            <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
            <span class="img-ph-desc">CAD/CAM machine in use, or Dr. Fu placing crown</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" style="margin-top:48px">
          <span class="tag">Common questions</span>
          <h2 class="prose" style="margin-top:8px">Good to know.</h2>
          <div class="faq">
            <details open><summary>How long do crowns and bridges last?</summary><p>With proper care, crowns and bridges can last 10-15 years or longer. Regular dental visits and good oral hygiene are key to their longevity.</p></details>
            <details><summary>Are crowns and bridges noticeable?</summary><p>We use tooth-colored materials that match your natural teeth closely, making crowns and bridges virtually indistinguishable from your own smile.</p></details>
            <details><summary>Is the procedure painful?</summary><p>We numb the area thoroughly to ensure your comfort during preparation and placement. Most patients report minimal discomfort.</p></details>
            <details><summary>Can I eat normally with crowns or bridges?</summary><p>Yes. Once placed, crowns and bridges function like natural teeth, allowing you to eat, speak, and smile confidently.</p></details>
            <details><summary>Will my insurance cover crowns and bridges?</summary><p>Many dental plans cover crowns and bridges partially. We'll help you understand your benefits and provide clear cost estimates upfront.</p></details>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <aside>
        <div class="scard reveal">
          <div class="hd"><div class="grid-ov"></div><h3>Ask about crowns &amp; bridges</h3><p>Same-day crowns available for qualifying cases</p></div>
          <div class="bd">
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg><span>Most crown appointments 60–90 min</span></div>
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg><span>Most insurance accepted &amp; verified</span></div>
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.5 9 8 11 4.5-2 8-6 8-11V5l-8-3z"/></svg><span>CAD/CAM precision technology</span></div>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <a class="btn" href="/contact">Ask About Crowns &amp; Bridges</a>
            <a class="btn btn-out" href="tel:7148932106" style="justify-content:center">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<ServiceExplore />

</Layout>
